snippet.title: Secrets Of The Dark 4: The Flower Of Shadow BETA
snippet.description: On his daughter's 16th birthday, his daughter gets an unidentified gift and she opens it, after she opens it a strange dark figure kidnaps her and seals off her room door and the door to the house.
